gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Timberwolves 111, Nuggets 98
gameRecap.excerpt: Minnesota defeats Denver, 111-98. For Minnesota, Anthony Edwards led the way with 25 points, five rebounds, and five assists while aided by Mike Conley (23 points, eight assists) in the victory. Nikola Jokic finished with 32 points, 10 rebounds, and five assists for Denver in the losing effort. Minnesota improves to 51-22, while Denver moves to 51-23 in the loss.
